      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KOTA LAMBAI (1) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at Murray Bridge Straight over 300m behind Hayden's Milk (17.69) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money the start prior. Should be very hard to beat this time. INTEGRATOR (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (19.97) at this track behind Cabao Marble in a Other. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and eight minor placings to his credit. Must be included in calculations. GOLDEN GANGSTER (5) took advantage of the inside draw with an all-the-way win last start (19.85) at this track in a Other over 342m. Sure to be thereabouts. ASTON BAKER (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
